Date: Thu, 16 Oct 2025 16:21:29 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: qcom: sm8250-samsung-common: correct reserved
 pins
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bsc#1012628
